es.ull.isaatc.function
Class UniformlyDistributedSplitFunction

java.lang.Object
  es.ull.isaatc.function.TimeFunction
      es.ull.isaatc.function.UniformlyDistributedSplitFunction

public class UniformlyDistributedSplitFunction
extends TimeFunction

Defines a time function which consists of an array of other time functions. The time unit is used to choose the function corresponding to the current timestamp. Therefore, getValue will return a value of part[i], where i = (ts / timeUnit) % functionArray.length

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
